<!DOCTYPE html>

<div class="upload-content" id="upload-content" style="width:25%;">
  <div id="upload-content-header">
    <p class="big-font no-margin">อัพโหลดไฟล์โมเดล</p>
  </div>
  <hr align="center" width="100%">
  <p>นามสกุลไฟล์ที่รองรับ</p>
  <ul>
    <li>.obj</li>
    <li>.stl</li>
  </ul>
  <form action="/upload" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
    <input name="order[model]" type="hidden" value="<%= @order.cached_model_data %>">
    <label for="model-upload" class="custom-file-upload">เลือกไฟล์</label>
    <input id="model-upload" name="order[model]" accept=".stl, .obj" type="file"></br></br>
    <label for="printing-material">เลือกวัสดุ</label></br>
    <select id="printing-material" name="order[printing_material]">
      <option value="abs_black" selected>ABS Black</option>
      <option value="abs_white">ABS White</option>
      <option value="pla_black">PLA Black</option>
      <option value="pla_white">PLA White</option>
    </select></br></br>
    <p>ความเร็วในการปริ้นท์</p>
    <input type="radio" name="order[printing_speed]" id="regular_speed" value="regular" checked/><label for="regular_speed">ธรรมดา</label>
    <input type="radio" name="order[printing_speed]" id="express_speed" value="express" /><label for="express_speed">ด่วน</label>
    </br></br>
    <p>ตัวเลือกการจัดส่ง</p>
    <input type="radio" name="order[delivery_method]" id="regular_speed" value="regular" checked/><label for="regular_speed">ธรรมดา</label>
    <input type="radio" name="order[delivery_method]" id="express_speed" value="express" /><label for="express_speed">ด่วน</label>
    </br></br>
    <input name="order[printing_size]" type="hidden" value="100%">
    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
  </form>
</div>

<h3>should be</h3>
<ol>
  <li>show box "choose model file"</li>
  <li>user click "choose"</li>
  <li>user choose model on computer</li>
  <li>user click ok in file picker</li>
  <li>div "upload-content" change innerHTML to model viewer without actually uploading the file</li>
  <li>model viewer controls = 3d model preview + printing option</li>
  <li>user select printing options</li>
  <li>calculate price</li>
  <li>user click "submit order"</li>
</ol>
